title: Watch: Try Not To Laugh Challenge, Rock/Metal Edition [News]
text:
Posted 9 hours ago 3 
A fun little video has surfaced via Blend Guitar, featuring the rock and metal edition of the whole try not to laugh challenge thing. 
The uploader noted: "I bet you a million bucks you won't win this CHALLENGE LOL. I saw a lot of 'try not to laugh challenge' lately so I made this rock and metal version."
